name: ext_R4_BiologicallyDerivedProduct
title: Cross-version Extension for R4.BiologicallyDerivedProduct for use in FHIR R2
description: This cross-version extension represents BiologicallyDerivedProduct from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/BiologicallyDerivedProduct|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R2.

element.short: A material substance originating from a biological entity
element.definition:
A material substance originating from a biological entity intended to be transplanted or infused
into another (possibly the same) biological entity.
